EnExplanation: A phrase used to introduce an example or illustration.

Samples.EeSentence: Ma toon sulle näite, näiteks raamatust.
Samples.EnSentence: I will give you an example, for instance from the book.

Samples.EeSentence: Ma tuletan sulle meelde, et see on ainult näiteks.
Samples.EnSentence: I remind you that this is just an example.
